<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bwmc Unfiltered</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hamburger-menu">‚ò∞</div>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img id="logo" src="image.jpg" alt="Logo Placeholder">
            <h2>Bwmc Unfiltered</h2>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home" class="nav-link active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about" class="nav-link">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#discussions" class="nav-link">Discussions</a></li>
                <li><a href="#friends" class="nav-link">Friends</a></li>
                <li><a href="#groups" class="nav-link">Groups</a></li>
                <li><button id="settings-btn" class="nav-btn">Settings</button></li>
                <li><button id="change-profile-btn" class="nav-btn">Profile</button></li>
                <li><button id="open-post-modal" class="nav-btn">Create Post</button></li>
                <li><button id="open-story-modal" class="nav-btn">Add Story</button></li>
                <li><a href="#messages" class="nav-link">Messages</a></li>
                <li><button id="logout-btn" class="nav-btn">Logout</button></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="main-content">
        <div id="home-section">
            <header>
                <h1>Bwmc Unfiltered</h1>
                <p class="tagline">Not Your Regular College Board</p>
            </header>
            <div class="stories-container">
                <div class="add-story-btn">
                    <div class="add-story-icon">+</div>
                    <p>Add Story</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="filters">
                <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
                <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="friends">Friends</button>
                <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="groups">Groups</button>
            </div>
            <div class="posts">
                <div class="post-card" data-post-id="1" data-username="User1" data-group="none">
                    <div class="post-header">
                        <span class="post-username">User1</span>
                        <span class="post-tag">Campus Buzz</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-content">Excited for the upcoming fest! üéâ</div>
                    <div class="post-image-container"></div>
                    <div class="post-reactions">
                        <button class="reaction-btn like-btn" data-liked="false">‚ù§Ô∏è <span class="like-count">0</span></button>
                        <button class="reaction-btn dislike-btn" data-disliked="false">üëé <span class="dislike-count">0</span></button>
                        <button class="reaction-btn comment-btn">üí¨ <span class="comment-count">0</span></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-comments">
                        <div class="comments-list"></div>
                        <div class="comment-input">
                            <input type="text" class="comment-text" placeholder="Add a comment...">
                            <button class="submit-comment">Post</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="follow-btn">Follow</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="about-section" style="display: none;">
            <div class="about-container">
                <header>
                    <h1>About Bwmc Unfiltered</h1>
                    <p class="tagline">Connecting the College Community</p>
                </header>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>Bwmc Unfiltered is a vibrant platform designed to bring college students together, fostering open communication, creativity, and community engagement. We aim to provide a space where you can share your thoughts, stories, and experiences without filters.</p>
                    <h2>Features</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Share posts and stories with your peers</li>
                        <li>Engage in real-time discussions</li>
                        <li>Connect through private messages</li>
                        <li>Customize your profile and experience</li>
                        <li>Stay updated, anytime, anywhere</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>Have questions or feedback? Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:rehanarahman004@gmail.com">rehanarahman.com</a>
                        <a href="divyashree28123@gmail.com">divyashree.com</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="discussions-section" style="display: none;">
            <div class="discussions-container">
                <header>
                    <h1>Discussions</h1>
                    <p class="tagline">Join the conversation in real-time!</p>
                </header>
                <div class="discussion-list">
                    <div class="discussion-message"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="discussion-input">
                    <input type="text" id="discussion-text" placeholder="Type your message...">
                    <button id="send-discussion">Send</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="friends-section" style="display: none;">
            <div class="friends-container">
                <header>
                    <h1>Friends</h1>
                    <p class="tagline">Connect with your college buddies!</p>
                </header>
                <button id="add-friend-btn" class="nav-btn">Add Friend</button>
                <div class="friends-list"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="groups-section" style="display: none;">
            <div class="groups-container">
                <header>
                    <h1>Groups</h1>
                    <p class="tagline">Join or create communities!</p>
                </header>
                <button id="manage-group-btn" class="nav-btn">Manage Groups</button>
                <div class="groups-list"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="messages-section" style="display: none;">
            <div class="messages-container">
                <div class="conversation-list">
                    <h3>Conversations</h3>
                    <div class="conversation" data-user="User1">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="User1">
                        <span>User1</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="conversation" data-user="User2">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="User2">
                        <span>User2</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="chat-window">
                    <h3 id="chat-username">Select a conversation</h3>
                    <div class="dm-list"></div>
                    <div class="dm-input">
                        <input type="text" id="dm-text" placeholder="Type a message...">
                        <button id="send-dm">Send</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="profile-section" style="display: none;">
            <div class="profile-page">
                <div class="profile-view">
                    <div class="profile-logo-container">
                        <img id="profile-dp-view" src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Profile Logo">
                        <div class="profile-info">
                            <h2 id="username-view">YourUsername</h2>
                            <p id="bio-view">Your bio goes here...</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-update">
                    <h3>Update Your Profile</h3>
                    <label for="username">Username:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Enter new username">
                    <label for="profile-dp">Profile Logo:</label>
                    <input type="file" id="profile-dp" accept="image/*">
                    <label for="bio">Bio:</label>
                    <textarea id="bio" placeholder="Tell us about yourself"></textarea>
                    <button id="save-profile">Save Profile</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="story-viewer">
        <div id="story-progress">
            <div id="story-progress-bar"></div>
        </div>
        <img id="story-content" src="" alt="Story">
    </div>
    <div id="post-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">√ó</span>
            <h2>Create Post</h2>
            <textarea id="post-text" placeholder="What's on your mind?"></textarea>
            <input type="file" id="post-image" accept="image/*">
            <img id="post-image-preview" src="" alt="Image Preview" style="display: none; max-width: 100%; margin: 0.5rem 0;">
            <select id="post-group" style="margin: 0.75rem 0;">
                <option value="none">No Group</option>
            </select>
            <button id="submit-post">Post</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="story-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">√ó</span>
            <h2>Add Story</h2>
            <input type="file" id="story-image" accept="image/*">
            <button id="submit-story">Share Story</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="settings-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">√ó</span>
            <h2>Settings</h2>
            <h3>Theme</h3>
            <label for="theme-select">Select Theme:</label>
            <select id="theme-select">
                <option value="light">Light</option>
                <option value="dark">Dark</option>
            </select>
            <button id="save-settings">Save</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="friend-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">√ó</span>
            <h2>Add Friend</h2>
            <input type="text" id="friend-username" placeholder="Enter username">
            <button id="submit-friend">Add Friend</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="group-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">√ó</span>
            <h2>Manage Groups</h2>
            <input type="text" id="group-name" placeholder="Enter group name">
            <button id="create-group">Create Group</button>
            <button id="join-group">Join Group</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="toast">Action successful!</div>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>